<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Document Legalization</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The document legalization process is the last step of the process and involves having your document legalized by the embassy or consulate of the destination country.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="http://localhost:8894/gform-test/" data-type="page" data-id="119">Add a link</a></p>
